\c 6
\s UDaniyeli usemgodini wezilwane
\p
\v 1 Kwaba kuhle kuDariyusi ukubeka phezu kombuso\x + 4.2.\x* iziphathamandla\x + 6.2-4; 6.6,7; 3.2.\x* ezilikhulu lamatshumi amabili\x + Esta 1.1.\x*, ukuthi zibe phezu kombuso wonke,
\v 2 laphezu kwazo ababonisi abathathu\x + 5.7.\x*, uDaniyeli aba ngowokuqala kubo\x + 6.3,4,6,7.\x*; ukuthi leziziphathamandla zilandise kubo\x + 6.2-4; 6.6,7; 3.2.\x*, njalo inkosi ingabi lomonakalo.
\v 3 Khona uDaniyeli lo wenza ngcono\x + Esta 2.9; Joha. 1.15,27,30; Roma 12.10.\x* kulababonisi\x + 6.3,4,6,7.\x* leziphathamandla\x + 6.2-4; 6.6,7; 3.2.\x*, ngoba umoya owedlulisileyo wawukuye\x + 5.12.\x*. Njalo inkosi yacabanga ukumbeka phezu kombuso wonke\x + Gen. 41.40; Esta 10.3.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Khona ababonisi\x + 6.3,4,6,7.\x* leziphathamandla\x + 6.2-4; 6.6,7; 3.2.\x* badinga ukuthola ithuba bemelene loDaniyeli mayelana lombuso\x + Tshu. 4.4.\x*; kodwa bengelakho ukuthola ithuba kumbe insolo\x + 2.9.\x*; ngoba wayethembekile\x + 2.40.\x*, futhi kungelampambaniso\x + 3.29.\x* kumbe insolo\x + 2.9.\x* okwatholakala kuye.
\v 5 Khona lawomadoda athi: Kasiyikuthola thuba ngaye lo uDaniyeli ngaphandle kokuthi si\add li\add*thole limelene laye emlayweni kaNkulunkulu wakhe\x + 6.7,12; 2.11.\x*.
\v 6 Khona labobabonisi\x + 6.3,4,6,7.\x* leziphathamandla\x + 6.2-4; 6.6,7; 3.2.\x* babuthana ndawonye enkosini, batsho kanje kuyo: Dariyusi nkosi, phila kuze kube nininini\x + 6.21; 2.4.\x*!
\v 7 Bonke ababonisi bombuso\x + 6.21; 2.4.\x*, izinduna\x + 2.48.\x*, leziphathamandla\x + 6.2-4; 6.6,7; 3.2.\x*, abeluleki\x + 3.24.\x*, lababusi\x + Ezra 5.14.\x* bacebisa ukumisa umthetho wesikhosini, lokwenza isimiso esiqinileyo, ukuthi loba ngubani ozacela isicelo lakuwuphi unkulunkulu loba umuntu phakathi kwezinsuku ezingamatshumi amathathu ngaphandle kuwe, nkosi, uzaphoselwa ebhalwini lwezilwane\x + 6.7,12; 2.11.\x*.
\v 8 Khathesi, nkosi, misa umlayo uphawule umbhalo, ukuthi ungaguqulwa, njengokomthetho\x + Esta 1.19; 8.8; Dan. 6.12,15; Esta 2.1.\x* wamaMede lamaPerisiya\x + 6.12,15; 5.28; 8.20; Esta 1.3,14,18,19; Dan.6.28.\x*, ongadluliyo\x + Esta 1.19; 8.8; Dan.6.12,15; Esta 2.1.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho inkosi uDariyusi yaphawula umbhalo lesimiso\x + 2.12.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Kwathi lapho uDaniyeli asesazi ukuthi umbhalo uphawuliwe, wangena endlini yakhe; njalo amawindi ekamelo lakhe\x + 2 Sam. 18.33; 1 Kho. 17.19,23.\x* eliphezulu elikhangele eJerusalema\x + 1 Kho. 8.44,48; Hlab. 5.7; 28.2; 138.2; Jona 2.4.\x* evulekile\x + Hez. 40.16.\x*; waguqa ngamadolo akhe\x + Hlab. 95.6.\x* izikhathi ezintathu ngosuku\x + Hlab. 55.17.\x*, wakhuleka, wapha izibongo phambi kukaNkulunkulu wakhe\x + 2.23.\x*, njengokwenza kwakhe mandulo kwalokhu\x + 2.23.\x*.
\v 11 Khona la amadoda abuthana, athola uDaniyeli ekhuleka encenga phambi kukaNkulunkulu wakhe.
\v 12 Khona asondela\x + 3.8.\x*, akhuluma phambi kwenkosi mayelana lesimiso senkosi \add athi\add*: Kawuphawulanga isimiso yini, sokuthi wonke umuntu ocela lakuwuphi unkulunkulu loba umuntu phakathi kwezinsuku ezingamatshumi amathathu\x + 6.7.\x* ngaphandle kuwe, nkosi\x + 6.5.\x*, uzaphoselwa ebhalwini lwezilwane? Inkosi yaphendula yathi: Linto iliqiniso, ngokomthetho wamaMede lamaPerisiya\x + 6.8.\x* ongadluliyo\x + 6.8.\x*.
\v 13 Khona aphendula athi phambi kwenkosi: UDaniyeli ongowabantwana bokuthunjwa bakoJuda\x + 1.6.\x*\x + 2.25.\x* kakunanzi\x + 3.12.\x*, nkosi, lesimiso osiphawulileyo, kodwa uyakhuleka isicelo sakhe izikhathi ezintathu ngosuku.
\v 14 Kwathi lapho inkosi isizwile lelilizwi, yazizondela kakhulu\x + Mark. 6.26.\x*, yabeka ingqondo kuDaniyeli ukumkhulula; yebo, yalwisa laze latshona ilanga ukumophula.
\v 15 Khona abuthana enkosini lawomadoda, athi enkosini: Yazi, nkosi, ukuthi umthetho wamaMede lamaPerisiya\x + 6.8.\x* uthi: Kakulasimiso kumbe umthetho inkosi eyawumisayo ongaguqulwa.
\v 16 Khona inkosi yalaya, bamletha uDaniyeli, ba\add m\add*phosela ebhalwini lwezilwane. Inkosi yaphendula yathi kuDaniyeli: UNkulunkulu wakho, omkhonzayo njalonjalo, kungathi angakukhulula\x + 6.20; Seb. 27.23.\x*!
\v 17 Kwasekulethwa ilitshe, labekwa phezu komlomo wobhalu\x + Lilo 3.53.\x*; inkosi yasilinameka\x + Mat. 27.66; Isam. 20.3; Jer. 32.10.\x* ngendandatho elophawu lwayo\x + Esta 3.12.\x*, langendandatho elophawu lwamakhosi ayo\x + 5.1.\x*, ukuze kungaguqulwa ulutho mayelana loDaniyeli.
\p
\v 18 Khona inkosi yaya esigodlweni sayo, yachitha ubusuku izila ukudla; lamachacho kawalethwanga phambi kwayo\x + Zaga 25.20.\x*; lobuthongo bayibalekela\x + Esta 6.1; Dan.2.1.\x*.
\v 19 Khona inkosi yavuka emadabukakusa\x + Zaga 4.18.\x*, yaya ngokuphangisa ebhalwini lwezilwane\x + 2.25.\x*.
\v 20 Yathi isisondele ebhalwini, yamemeza ngelizwi lokulila kuDaniyeli; inkosi yaphendula yathi kuDaniyeli: Daniyeli, nceku kaNkulunkulu ophilayo\x + 6.26.\x*, uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 3.15.\x* omkhonzayo njalonjalo\x + 6.20; Seb. 27.23.\x*, ulakho ukukukhulula yini ezilwaneni?
\v 21 Khona uDaniyeli wathi enkosini: Nkosi, phila kuze kube nininini\x + 6.6.\x*!
\v 22 UNkulunkulu wami uthumile ingilosi yakhe\x + 3.28.\x*, yavala \add imi\add*lomo yezilwane, okokuthi kazingilimazanga\x + Heb. 11.33; Hlab. 22.21; 57.4.\x*, ngoba phambi kwakhe ukungabi lecala kutholakale kimi\x + 2.40.\x*; njalo phambi kwakho, nkosi, kangenzanga bubi.
\v 23 Khona inkosi yamthokozela kakhulu, yalaya ukukhuphula uDaniyeli ebhalwini. UDaniyeli wasekhutshulwa ebhalwini, kakwatholwa kulimala kuye\x + 3.25.\x*, ngoba ekholwe kuNkulunkulu wakhe\x + Heb. 11.33.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Inkosi yasilaya, kwasekulethwa lawomadoda\x + Dute. 19.19.\x* ayehlebe uDaniyeli\x + 3.8.\x*, bawaphosela ebhalwini lwezilwane, wona, abantwana bawo, labomkawo\x + Esta 9.10.\x*; kwathi bengakafiki phansi ebhalwini, izilwane zazibusa phezu kwabo, zachoboza wonke amathambo abo.
\p
\v 25 Khona inkosi uDariyusi yabalela bonke abantu, izizwe, lezindimi\x + 4.1.\x*, ezihlezi emhlabeni wonke\x + 4.1.\x*, \add yathi\add*: Kakwandiswe ukuthula kwenu\x + 4.1.\x*.
\v 26 Umlayo wenziwa yimi\x + 3.29.\x*, ukuthi kukho konke ukubuswa kombuso wami bathuthumele\x + 5.19; Hlab. 99.1.\x* besabe\x + 5.19; Hlab. 99.1.\x* phambi kukaNkulunkulu kaDaniyeli; ngoba enguNkulunkulu ophilayo\x + 4.34; Ruthe 1.16; Ezra 1.3.\x*\x + 6.20; Hlab. 42.2.\x*, lomi kuze kube nininini, lombuso wakhe\x + Hlab. 10.16; 2.44.\x* ngongayikuchithwa\x + Hlab. 10.16; 2.44.\x*, lokubusa kwakhe kuzakuba khona kuze kube sekupheleni\x + 7.26.\x*.
\v 27 Uyakhulula, ophule, enze izibonakaliso lezimangaliso emazulwini lemhlabeni\x + 4.2.\x*, osekhulule uDaniyeli emandleni ezilwane\x + 3.29.\x*.
\v 28 Ngakho uDaniyeli lo waphumelela embusweni kaDariyusi\x + 3.30.\x*, lembusweni\x + 1.21.\x* kaKoresi umPerisiya\x + Ezra 1.1,2; 4.5; 6.14; 10.1; 2 Lan. 36.20; 5.28; Dan.6.8.\x*.
